{"tid":1545472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所以話，幾時都叫手足出街記住戴口罩同長遮","createTime":"2019-09-06T02:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T04:53:55.000Z","uid":280136,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"08d3e0c3ced4db9dcc8e7ac6a4e8f36303a279a6","tid":1545472,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:24:59.000Z","msg":"話說小弟啱啱搭地鐵<br />\n<br />\n對面坐左隻廢中返緊支國，係度滔滔不絕吹到自己天花龍鳳咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一貫藍絲嘅講法，係美國又點點點，係大陸又點點點<br />\n<br />\n又話自己如果後生廿年一定幫拖打人，報警乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n又係D收錢論啊、想要安寧嘅廢柴<br />\n<br />\n咁我就臨落車果下屌柒左件垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住佢起身想開我拖<br />\n<br />\n我即刻大聲兇左佢一句「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係咪想沃手啊！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n條廢柴即刻龜縮熬底，完全冇佢之前嘅「大將之風」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以話，乜時候都要準備狗罩同長遮<br />\n<br />\n狗罩用黎保護自己以免比D廢老影大頭<br />\n<br />\n長遮用黎保護自己避免比人打<br />\n<br />\n見到廢老想沃手，大聲兇尻條垃圾就得<br />\n<br />\n大多數都係講就兇狠，做就碌撚嘅垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我屌柒件垃圾唔會對佢造成傷害，睇住佢衝過黎又比我兇返轉頭個樣真係好笑到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢返到大陸肯定又一肚火唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3254f9e22fa328a6ec496e53c0f6a0aba2e544","tid":1545472,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:25:11.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8768e92024e43b0b30a5b2ee84ac52b233f0f833","tid":1545472,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:25:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">還我 831 真相！不要港版 64！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［還我 831 真相］點解口吐白沫？原因在此！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544189</a></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">大個仔</span>獨立必睇</span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9 大核彈<span style=\"font-size: small;\">內容包括</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">：</span></span></span><br />\n(1) 基本法自古以來是中國領土的謬誤<br />\n(2) 中英聯合聲明的謬誤<br />\n(3) 不平等條約無效論是謊言<br />\n(4) 中華民國早已放棄香港的主權<br />\n(5) 中華人民共和國以武力脅迫大英國移交香港主權不合國際法<br />\n(6) 70年代聯合國從非自治領名單剔除香港<br />\n(7) 中英聯合聲明違反住民自決原則<br />\n(8) 香港符合《蒙特維多國家權利及義務公約》中「國家」的定義<br />\n(9) 香港軍事史<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></s